rComments: I have no idea what the other person is talking about.  Professor Zeamer is my hero!  She inspired me to change my major to community studies in her social justice class.  She is funny and tough, but fair.

Do not take her class!!! Don't do it or else you will regret it. She does not make any sense when giving you feed back on your essays. She starts with one thing you go fix it and resubmit. When she grades it again she tells you something completely different. She seems like she doesn't know what she's teaching.
